      },
      {
        "_key": "inline-link-29c5f782-1637-4714-86d3-339fcaf265fc",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "inline-pr-8ccc35e0-6d13-4fd5-ab59-327144810b45",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "[PR] "
          },
          {
            "_key": "inline-link-text-3f57f42f-29d5-4305-8a69-dac88138baf1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "Amazonで看護助手グッズを探す"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block--8446521892015027344",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-373389077394698207",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "まとめ"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-2a124b27-ee23-4024-bb7f-670c2521e05c",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-6246353c-e405-4235-8068-2d1eab2e0e90",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "感染対策の基本｜標準予防策と手洗いの重要性でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-95e8e91a-ab7a-4289-ab3f-0ae133f28824",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-816fedc9-e949-49d1-be69-bfa0dd402907",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-6123b623-36c2-4ab2-8b9d-ae6d575926bf",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-005827ad-b5aa-48ef-a538-12864e119672",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "患者さんの安全を守る：感染症の拡大を防ぎ、患者さんの回復をサポートします。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-0f467449-2102-46e4-a43d-d4c5ab6a3e01",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-68f51cf1-de07-4f32-95c8-558f48cad1a5",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
